module: b1-16
level: B1
sequence: 16
slug: motion-verbs-full-system
version: '2.0'
title: 'Дієслова руху: повна система'
subtitle: Motion Verbs - The Full System
content_outline:
- section: Вступ
  points:
  - Introduction to motion verb system — align with State Standard §4.2.3.1 (conjugation)
    and §4.2.2.4 (Accusative directionality)
  - 'Overview of unidirectional vs multidirectional — use ''Vector vs Circle'' visual
    analogy: Unidirectional (Arrow →) vs Multidirectional (Circle/Chaos ↺)'
- section: Пояснення
  points:
  - 14 motion verb pairs explained — highlight high-frequency pairs like лізти/лазити
    (literal/figurative) and тягти/тягати (physical effort)
  - 'Usage patterns — learner error: The ''Round Trip'' Trap (using unidirectional
    for completed trips); learner error: Vehicle vs Foot confusion (strict separation
    of йти vs їхати); address ''Adverbial Blindness'' (keywords like часто, завжди
    demand multidirectional)'
- section: Практика
  points:
  - 'Decision-making exercises — cultural hook: Logistics of the ''Breadbasket'' (grain
    to ports) requiring везти/возити and пливти'
  - 'Context selection — cultural hook: Nova Poshta & Ukrzaliznytsia as icons of motion
    (їздити, розвозити)'
- section: Діалоги
  points:
  - 'Motion verbs in conversation — theme: ''Iron Diplomacy'' (Залізна дипломатія)
    using їздити for trains'
  - Natural usage — include proverb 'Під лежачий камінь вода не тече' (Water doesn't
    flow under a lying stone)
vocabulary_hints:
  required:
  - односпрямований (unidirectional)
  - різноспрямований (multidirectional)
  - йти/ходити (to go on foot) — strict distinction from vehicle transport
  - 'їхати/їздити (to go by vehicle) — context: Ukrzaliznytsia trains'
  - бігти/бігати (to run)
  - летіти/літати (to fly)
  - 'пливти/плавати (to swim/sail) — context: grain ships sailing to ports'
  - нести/носити (to carry)
  - вести/водити (to lead)
  - 'везти/возити (to transport) — context: trucking logistics (фури) and grain export'
  recommended:
  - 'лізти/лазити (to climb) — collocations: лізти вгору, лізти в кишеню, лазити в
    інтернеті'
  - 'повзти/повзати (to crawl) — collocations: туман повзе, чутки повзуть, дитина
    повзає'
  - 'тягти/тягати (to pull) — collocations: тягти час (stall), тягати залізо (gym
    slang)'
  - котити/качати (to roll)
  - 'брести/бродити (to wade) — collocations: бродити по лісу, думки бродять'
activity_hints:
- type: match-up
  focus: Unidirectional → Multidirectional pairs
  items: 14+
- type: quiz
  focus: Which motion verb for which context?
  items: 15+
- type: fill-in
  focus: Choose correct motion verb
  items: 15+
- type: true-false
  focus: Single trip vs regular/general movement
  items: 14+
- type: fill-in
  focus: Single event → habitual movement
  items: 10+
focus: grammar
pedagogy: TTT
